QuestData.Title: The Anglers
QuestData.Description: If you want to explore all the secrets of the deep ocean, and catch some big fish, speak to Haito at the Anglers Wharf in Krasarang Wilds.$B$BI'm sure he'd love to show you a thing or two about reeling!
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak to Fisherman Haito at the Anglers Wharf in the Krasarang Wilds.
